        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Repair or replace the vehicle speed sensor"
        },
        {
          "id": "n3",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Check input signal\n1. Start engine\n2. Select \"DATA MONITOR\"\n   \u2022 Read \"CAR SPEED SENSOR\" value while driving\n   \u2022 Check the value changes according to driving speed\n   \u2014 OR \u2014\n   Check voltage between N-CVT control unit terminal # 7 and # 16 while driving (Measure in A/C range)\n   Voltage: min. 5V at 30 km/h\n   (the voltage rises gradually in response to vehicle speed)"
        },
        {
          "id": "n4",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Check harness continuity between N-CVT control unit and vehicle speed sensor"
        },
        {
          "id": "n5",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Perform self diagnosis again after test drive."
        },
        {
          "id": "n6",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "1. Check N-CVT control unit I/O signal\n2. Re-check N-CVT control unit pin terminals for damage or incorrect connection of control unit harness connector"
